<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤١٤ - حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3919">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مَسْلَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4340">عَدِيِّ بْنِ ثَابِتٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3988">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ يَزِيدَ الْخَطْمِيِّ، </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1731">أَبَا أَيُّوبَ </a>أَخْبَرَهُ: <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ صَلَّى مَعَ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فِي حَجَّةِ الْوَدَاعِ الْمَغْرِبَ وَالْعِشَاءَ جَمِيعًا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>